---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  lang="en"
  title="Printing services — stickers, labels, digital printing | WIPP Białystok"
  description="We offer printing of stickers, self-adhesive labels, Data Matrix codes, business cards, flyers, posters, and custom t-shirts. WIPP Printing House Białystok."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-12 md:pt-32 md:pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-800 to-blue-950 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4">Printing services</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-blue-100">From Data Matrix codes to business cards — we handle every order.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 space-y-16">

      <!-- Data Matrix -->
      <div class="md:flex gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v1m6 11h2m-6 0h-2v4m0-11v3m0 0h.01M12 12h4.01M16 20h4M4 12h4m12 0h.01M5 8h2a1 1 0 001-1V5a1 1 0 00-1-1H5a1 1 0 00-1 1v2a1 1 0 001 1zm12 0h2a1 1 0 001-1V5a1 1 0 00-1-1h-2a1 1 0 00-1 1v2a1 1 0 001 1zM5 20h2a1 1 0 001-1v-2a1 1 0 00-1-1H5a1 1 0 00-1 1v2a1 1 0 001 1z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Data Matrix codes — product marking</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Our leading specialty. The client provides us with files containing unique Data Matrix codes,
            and we print them on stickers in the required order and layout — both individual labels
            and aggregation codes on bulk packages.
          </p>
          <a href="/en/data-matrix/" class="text-blue-700 font-semibold hover:underline">Learn more about Data Matrix codes &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-gray-200" />

      <!-- Stickers -->
      <div class="md:flex gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A2 2 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Stickers and self-adhesive labels</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Printing on self-adhesive paper, transparent foil, matte foil, and other specialty materials.
            Product labels, promotional stickers, barcodes, security stickers.
            We handle both short and long runs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-gray-200" />

      <!-- Digital printing -->
      <div class="md:flex gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 17h2a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h6a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2zm8-12V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4h10z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Digital and offset printing</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Business cards, flyers, posters, brochures, catalogues, letterheads. Printing on offset paper,
            coated paper, and cardboard. Even small runs with express 24-48h option.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-gray-200" />

      <!-- T-shirts -->
      <div class="md:flex gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Custom printed t-shirts</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            T-shirt printing, iron-on transfers, clothing personalization. We handle orders
            starting from just one piece — perfect for teams, school classes, companies, and events.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Have a non-standard order?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Non-standard orders are our specialty. Contact us — we'll advise and provide a quote.</p>
      <a href="/en/kontakt/" class="bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-800 transition-colors">
        Get a quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
